# CODEOWNERS file
# This file defines who owns specific parts of the codebase.
# When a PR modifies files in these directories, the specified owners
# will automatically be requested for review.

# Default owner for everything in the repository
# Replace @your-github-handle with your actual GitHub username
*       @your-github-handle

# Specific ownership for source files
# PRs that modify files in /src/ will require review from these owners
/src/   @your-github-handle

# You can add more specific ownership rules as needed, for example:
# /.github/workflows/   @devops-team
# /docs/                @documentation-team
